E keni pranuar menderisht,
.

00:37:00.791 --> 00:37:04.415
por nuk jeni bere akoma.

00:37:06.499 --> 00:37:10.415
Sepse projektimi mendor vjen nga mendimi;

00:37:11.874 --> 00:37:15.749
kjo do te thote se ju jeni ne nivelin e mendimit.

00:37:16.373 --> 00:37:20.249
Duhet te beheni pamendime.

00:37:21.791 --> 00:37:24.499
Por nese jeton ne bazen e mendimit

00:37:24.916 --> 00:37:28.791
atehere perseri i perket Cakres Agnya.

00:37:31.999 --> 00:37:34.999
Pra fillimisht duhet te ndalojme valen e mendimeve,

00:37:35.373 --> 00:37:39.957
dhe duhet te themi qe "Ne rregull, le te shohim si."

00:37:46.333 --> 00:37:49.291
Pra nga Cakra Nabhi ju ngjiteni

00:37:49.624 --> 00:37:52.791
te Cakra Agnya.

00:37:55.749 --> 00:38:00.373
Pastaj mbi te vjen problemi i trete shkaterrues,

00:38:00.665 --> 00:38:04.083
eshte emocional.

