Emocionali eshte shume delikat.
.

00:38:25.874 --> 00:38:28.041
Si disa njerez, Sahaja yogistet,

00:38:28.333 --> 00:38:29.999
do te ulen me nje kitare

00:38:30.373 --> 00:38:37.457
dhe do te fillojne te kendojne si te ishin zogj dashurie, kuptoni!

00:38:49.874 --> 00:38:53.083
C'eshte kjo? C'eshte kjo?

00:38:53.791 --> 00:38:57.749
Eja afer. Eja, eja...

00:38:58.041 --> 00:39:00.916
C'po ndodh?
.

00:39:01.957 --> 00:39:03.707
Pse, pse qani?

