saqe une Vete frikesohem prej tyre:

00:42:35.540 --> 00:42:37.333
Sa dine rreth Sahaja Yoga,

00:42:37.582 --> 00:42:40.540
Mendoj une ndonjehere?

00:42:52.499 --> 00:42:57.457
Dhe fillojne ta pohojne ate aq shume sa behet e frikeshme.

00:43:03.624 --> 00:43:07.291
E gjithe kjo mund edhe te thuhet, qe

00:43:07.665 --> 00:43:09.957
atyre i duket se protokolli nuk eshte si duhet

00:43:10.373 --> 00:43:11.749
dhe duhet te jete nje protokoll i pershtatshem,

00:43:12.083 --> 00:43:13.374
pra ne kujdesemi per protokollin,

00:43:13.707 --> 00:43:15.166
ne jemi roje te protokollit,

00:43:15.499 --> 00:43:18.540
e gjithe keto gjera.

00:43:24.415 --> 00:43:27.249
Tani ata qe jane ne anen emocionale

00:43:27.624 --> 00:43:30.874
shohin egon e te tjereve, ndersa ata qe jane ne anen e egos

00:43:31.291 --> 00:43:34.582
shohin emocionet e te tjereve.

00:43:42.083 --> 00:43:44.665
Pra njeri kritikon tjetrin,

00:43:46.832 --> 00:43:52.249
por ata nuk shohin veten e tyre qe jane duke rene ne nje kurth

00:43:52.540 --> 00:43:55.083
ne nje nga ekstremet.
.

00:43:59.041 --> 00:44:04.249
Pra pervec dhe derisa te jeni te shkeputur, ju s'mund ta kuptoni.
.

00:44:12.665 --> 00:44:14.624
S'do te them qe bera, kreva nje gabim,

00:44:14.957 --> 00:44:18.333
por ndodh qe te jete gabim.

00:44:21.791 --> 00:44:23.707
