00:44:41.540 --> 00:44:43.166
dhe i provoi gjithe hilet tantrike,

00:44:43.457 --> 00:44:46.124
ndaj mu desh te tregoja.

00:44:52.707 --> 00:44:56.791
Tani cdo Sahaja Yogi eshte nje pako fantazmash!

